SylNotify - 
=======================

generate notification plug-in for Sylpheed

Requirement
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Windows XP SP3
Windows 7 SP1
Sylpheed 3.1.2 or later

Install
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

1) copy sylnotify.dll to Sylpheed plugin directory.
2) copy sylnotify.mo to lib/locale/ja/LC_MESSAGES directory.
   
Usage
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Notice
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This plugin is not stable.
